 # Database Rules

## Schema Guidelines
- Use meaningful names in Spanish
- Follow Prisma naming conventions
- Implement proper relations
- Use appropriate field types
- Add proper indexes

## Main Entities
- Producto
- Cliente
- Usuario
- Sucursal
- OrdenCompra
- Factura
- CierreCaja

## Relationships
- Each Sucursal has many Usuarios
- Each OrdenCompra belongs to one Cliente
- Each Factura relates to one OrdenCompra